```scala
class Counter{
 private var value = 0
 def increment()( value +=1 )
 def current() = value
}
```
* 调用无参方法时可以在方法名结尾加上括号，也可以不加
```scala
val abc = new Counter;
abc.increment();
abc.increment;
```

#####也可以通过以下形式来强制调用时不写括号
```scala
class Counter{
 private var value = 0
 def increment()( value +=1 )
 def current = value //定义方法时就不写括号
}
```